  "rawHTML": "<p>加拿大 / 美国 / 中国房产投资的税务差异</p>\t\t\n\t\t<p>发表于：9/30/2023</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">投资房产一直是华人所热衷的，很多华人过去十几年除了在国内购置房产，也在美国、加拿大投资了房产。除了房产收益不一样，这三个国家对于房租收入的税收又是如何计算的呢？今天我们就来仔细对比分析下！</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"1256\" height=\"689\" src=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screenshot-2024-09-25-at-4.46.56 PM.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screenshot-2024-09-25-at-4.46.56 PM.png 1256w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screenshot-2024-09-25-at-4.46.56 PM-300x165.png 300w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screenshot-2024-09-25-at-4.46.56 PM-1024x562.png 1024w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screenshot-2024-09-25-at-4.46.56 PM-768x421.png 768w, https://lucrewisefin.10web.me/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Screenshot-2024-09-25-at-4.46.56 PM-600x329.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1256px) 100vw, 1256px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tEnvelope\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M464 64H48C21.49 64 0 85.49 0 112v288c0 26.51 21.49 48 48 48h416c26.51 0 48-21.49 48-48V112c0-26.51-21.49-48-48-48zm0 48v40.805c-22.422 18.259-58.168 46.651-134.587 106.49-16.841 13.247-50.201 45.072-73.413 44.701-23.208.375-56.579-31.459-73.413-44.701C106.18 199.465 70.425 171.067 48 152.805V112h416zM48 400V214.398c22.914 18.251 55.409 43.862 104.938 82.646 21.857 17.205 60.134 55.186 103.062 54.955 42.717.231 80.509-37.199 103.053-54.947 49.528-38.783 82.032-64.401 104.947-82.653V400H48z\"></path></svg>\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tExternal-link-square-alt\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg viewBox=\"0 0 448 512\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M448 80v352c0 26.51-21.49 48-48 48H48c-26.51 0-48-21.49-48-48V80c0-26.51 21.49-48 48-48h352c26.51 0 48 21.49 48 48zm-88 1